### 2. 생성자 패턴

#### new(): 표준 생성자

```rust
impl User {
    fn new(name: &str, age: u32) -> User {
        User {
            name: String::from(name),
            age,
        }
    }
}

let user = User::new("Alice", 25);
```

#### from_*(): 변환 생성자

```rust
impl Color {
    fn from_hex(hex: &str) -> Color {
        // hex 문자열 "FF0000"을 RGB (255, 0, 0)으로 변환
        Color { r: 255, g: 0, b: 0 }
    }
}

let red = Color::from_hex("FF0000");
```

#### 빌더 패턴 (Builder Pattern)

```rust
impl ConfigBuilder {
    fn new() -> ConfigBuilder {
        ConfigBuilder {
            timeout: 5000,
            retries: 3,
        }
    }

    fn with_timeout(mut self, timeout: u32) -> ConfigBuilder {
        self.timeout = timeout;
        self
    }

    fn build(self) -> Config {
        Config {
            timeout: self.timeout,
            retries: self.retries,
        }
    }
}

let config = ConfigBuilder::new()
    .with_timeout(10000)
    .build();
```

