## 📝 설계 패턴

### 패턴 1: 값 반환

```rust
impl User {
    fn email(&self) -> &str {
        &self.email
    }

    fn full_name(&self) -> String {
        format!("{} {}", self.first_name, self.last_name)
    }
}
```

### 패턴 2: 검증과 Result

```rust
impl BankAccount {
    fn withdraw(&mut self, amount: f64) -> Result<f64, String> {
        if amount <= 0.0 {
            return Err("양수만 출금 가능".to_string());
        }
        if self.balance < amount {
            return Err("잔액 부족".to_string());
        }
        self.balance -= amount;
        Ok(self.balance)
    }
}

match account.withdraw(100.0) {
    Ok(new_balance) => println!("남은 잔액: {}", new_balance),
    Err(e) => println!("오류: {}", e),
}
```

### 패턴 3: 상태 변경

```rust
impl State {
    fn transition(&mut self, event: Event) {
        self.current = match (self.current, event) {
            (State::Idle, Event::Start) => State::Running,
            (State::Running, Event::Stop) => State::Idle,
            (state, _) => state,  // 상태 유지
        };
    }
}
```

### 패턴 4: 컬렉션 조작

```rust
impl UserList {
    fn add(&mut self, user: User) {
        self.users.push(user);
    }

    fn find(&self, name: &str) -> Option<&User> {
        self.users.iter().find(|u| u.name == name)
    }

    fn count(&self) -> usize {
        self.users.len()
    }
}
```

